{"tid":1389791,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"示威嘅檢討","createTime":"2019-07-31T03:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T15:48:51.000Z","uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75610e7269d850aba2c2c743197ab7679ec6a663","tid":1389791,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:45:57.000Z","msg":"而家香港嘅示威，志在向政府表達訴求、令政府清晰聽到民意，並要求政府回應。<br />\n<br />\n而睇返西方國家嘅示威，係向政府發出最後通牒，可以話係威脅。<br />\n令政府知道如果唔完全接受民眾嘅要求，就等於與民為敵，民眾會有實際行動制裁政權。<br />\n<strong><ins>當政權表明唔會答應民眾要求，民眾嘅目標已經唔再係迫政府答應要求，而係要推翻呢個極權政府，由人民當家作主(即係民主)。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢到唔評論兩者嘅成效，只係想提下大家，香港嘅示威同西方國家唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727cd6e7c5c6f0bb754a6f08b8f6f3a9fc14d78d","tid":1389791,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:46:09.000Z","msg":"入黎睇下一齊呼籲罷工 幫手推<br />\n<br />\n有人為你衝，你肯唔肯為佢唔返工？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389755\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389755</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7968b3ef8a631f521cc6dd18b53278504631b27c","tid":1389791,"uid":101803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ed2c5a1a0b936896cd5fd62342cf96a8803b038","tid":1389791,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7968b3ef8a631f521cc6dd18b53278504631b27c","tid":1389791,"uid":101803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭人一開始都冇"},{"pid":"7f94eab466920f4e93b1d5f53696c6333b29b670","tid":1389791,"uid":101803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:37:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26b8d849f814ac11885f8751f624fba4e4938b3d","tid":1389791,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f94eab466920f4e93b1d5f53696c6333b29b670","tid":1389791,"uid":101803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ed2c5a1a0b9